Package com.example.rucafe

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Customizable
    Customizable is an interface that defines the common operations for Coffee item and all orders Implemented by Coffee, Orders, and StoreOrders
    MenuItem
    MenuItem is an interface that defines the common operations for all MenuItems Implemented by Coffee and Donut
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Coffee
    Coffee Class is a class that defines the properties that comes with an instance of a coffee and the corresponding methods that go with it.
    Donut
    Donut Class is a class that defines the properties that comes with an instance of a donut and the corresponding methods that go with it.
    DonutRecViewAdapter
    DonutRecViewAdapter Class is a class that gives the GUI a list of donuts with it's respective properties and the corresponding methods that go with it.
    DonutRecViewAdapter.ItemsHolder
    Get the views from the row layout file, similar to the onCreate() method.
    MainActivity
    This class is the Main GUI that has the buttons that lead to all the other GUIs
    Order
    Order Class is a class that takes in a list of MenuItems with their respective data
    OrderingBasketActivity
    This class is what controls all the actions for each button using the inputs given by the user in the orderingDonuts and orderingCoffee GUI
    OrderingCoffeeActivity
    This class is what controls all the actions for each button using the inputs given by the user in the orderingCoffee GUI
    OrderingDonutsActivity
    This class is what controls all the actions for each GUI components using the inputs given by the user in the orderingDonuts GUI
    StoreOrders
    Order Class is a class that takes in a Map of Orders with their respective data
    StoreOrdersActivity
    This class is what controls all the actions for each button using the inputs given by the user in the orderingDonuts, orderingCoffee, orderingBasket GUI
